  <text xml:lang="eng">
    <body>
      <div>
        <pb n="57" />
        <cb type="start" />
        <cb />
        <head>First World War or Second World War?</head>
        <p>1 It lasted the longest.</p>
        <p>2 Réunion was threatened by the Japanese.</p>
        <p>
          3 Réunionnais
          <note type="editorial" n="1">
            <p>Editor´s note: inhabitants of Réunion island.</p>
          </note>
          fought in the Balkans.
        </p>
        <p>4 Troops came ashore on Réunion.</p>
        <p>5 Fighting ended with an armistice on 11 November.</p>
        <p>
          6 It caused the most casualties among soldiers from Réunion.
          <note type="editorial" n="2">
            <p>Editor´s note: This sentence can also be translated as: ‚It caused more casualties among soldiers from Réunion.’</p>
          </note>
        </p>
        <p>7 This war was the most deadly for France.</p>
        <p>8 This war was the most deadly for humanity.</p>
        <p>
          Match each statement with the correct world war.
          <lb />
        </p>
      </div>
